name: FLYING ON ALL FOUR GENERATIONS OF THE BOEING 737 IN CANADA!
description:
At the start of 2018, I booked a return trip on Canadian North Airlines between Edmonton and Yellowknife to fly on their 737-200. Later in the year, I saw some great deals on Flair Airlines between Calgary and Winnipeg on their 737-400. With that, I made a goal to fly on all four generations (Original, Classic, Next Generation, MAX) in 2018, and I managed to do just that. See what it's like to fly on every generation of the world's best-selling airliner!

Thanks for watching!
